<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Galkap banga chieh in! Kristien sepaihte,
 I maua na chiehsa, Isu chuh en in;
 Krista I Lalpen un, galdo di'n ei pui,
 Kidona phuol achun; a puonlap a phe'i.
 Galkap banga chieh in Kristien sepaihte,
 I maua na chieh sa, Isu chuh enin.

[V2]
 2. Isu min I sap tieng, Setan gal a zam,
 Pangun, Kristien sepaih, galzo zel dingin;
 I pahchaknau Aw gin, gawtmun hihling ding,
 Suohpihte kiko un, ngeih takin lasau.

[V3]
 3. Sepaih tamtak bangin, Pathien Sapchuom um,
 Suohpihte mithieng haw, nungzui I hiu ui;
 I kikhen zak puou hi, pumkhat I hiu ui,
 I tup, I Thugin leh Hehpihna kibang.

[V4]
 4. Lalna a hung bei thei, Lalgam a tuoi thei,
 Mahleh Isu Sapchuom, um zing ding ahi;
 Gawtmun kulh kawtkhak te'n, Sapchuom zo ngei lo,
 Krista thutiem I nei; zie chuh thawn ngeilo.

[V5]
 5. Mipite, pang zelun, kei u lawi hung hiu,
 Lopi, chawihat zahna, Lal Krista chang hen;
 La ei hung sakpih un, galzawhna la chuh,
 Mihing leh Angel te'n, kumsawt in san au.</lyrics>
<title>ONWARD CHRISTIAN SOLDIERS!</title>
<hymn_number>299</hymn_number>
</song>